{"title":"阴影","slug":"shade","date":"2017-02-10T01:36:00.000Z","updated":"2017-04-13T15:11:18.079Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<h2 id=\"边框阴影\"><a href=\"#边框阴影\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"边框阴影\"></a>边框阴影</h2><figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.box</span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">box-shadow</span>:<span class=\"comment\">/*内部阴影*/</span>inset <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">20px</span> <span class=\"number\">#0f0</span>,<span class=\"comment\">/*外部阴影*/</span><span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">20px</span> <span class=\"number\">#f00</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"文字阴影\"><a href=\"#文字阴影\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文字阴影\"></a>文字阴影</h2><figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.box</span> <span class=\"selector-tag\">p</span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">text-shadow</span>:<span class=\"number\">1px</span> <span class=\"number\">1px</span> <span class=\"number\">2px</span> red;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">/*第一个为平行参数，第二个为垂直参数，第三个为模糊程度，第四个为颜色*/</span></div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","thumbnail":"/img/天使.jpg","primarycolor":"blueGrey","accentcolor":"blueGrey","categories":[{"name":"CSS3","path":"api/categories/CSS3.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS3","path":"api/tags/CSS3.json"},{"name":"阴影","path":"api/tags/阴影.json"}]}